channel.title: Um.. Is that Compile is normal?
channel.description:
Hello,
When I click on "compile". The black box appear and said "The system cannot find the path specified. Press any key to continue..."
Is that normal? The other TUT guide taught me, on end of topic. It's said "Save, Compile, Run Server". Hey, looks that Compile is important for me.. but why, compile doesn't looks good?
Help me, please! Thanks!
~Cheesy

item.title: Um.. Is that Compile is normal?
item.dc:creator: @Nets8 Nets8
item.description:
@Nets8 wrote:

What that means is that you specified the path in your Control Panel and the system couldn’t find something in the path. So pretty much, you need to change your path to the right one. Use the search button on the forums, there has to be something on it (even after the big pruneout).

Read full topic
